data.description: Nestled back into Lakes of Scarborough is where you'll find this updated 2-story with so much to love. Set on a partially wood, cul-de-sac lot you'll enjoy the quietness and shade of the mature trees. Inside and out the owners have loved on and update this home in and out, some of which include: New HVAC 2018, ALL exterior concrete replaced 2021, Master bath remodel 2022,  New windows 2013, Carpet above grade 2020, Garage doors 2019, Front ext siding 2022, Custom blinds 2021. FULL Kitchen remodeled 2021 with new custom - soft close cabinets, granite, under mount sink, back splash, fixtures, etc. Great room has wood burning fireplace with brick surround, custom built-ins, and open flow into dinette and kitchen is perfect for entertainment. Several additional living spaces with the front living room, dining/den, 2nd floor loft and finished rec room in the basement. Oversized two car garage, fenced in back yard, and yes the tree house stays! Call today to get your showing scheduled!
